INIT ASK a ANGLE a.
VAR b pd.
PEN DOWN.
PRINTMAFS (b*-1+180).
MOVE 8.
IF py < 8.
THEN ANGLE (b*-1+180) CLEAR.
IF py > 248.
THEN ANGLE (b*-1+180) CLEAR.
IF px < 8.
THEN ANGLE (b*-1) CLEAR.
IF px > 248.
THEN ANGLE (b*-1) CLEAR.
UNLESS px lim 0 256.
THEN PEN UP GOTO 128 128.
UNLESS py lim 0 256.
THEN PEN UP GOTO 128 128.